snippet.title: Masked Shooters Single-player Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Masked Shooters FPS in single-player.

You can create a room, choose your game mode, map, play in teams or free for all.

Masked Shooters features covert operational soldiers armed with advanced weaponry.

http://www.freezenova.com/
